215
00:13:00,393 --> 00:13:03,762
Oh...I know, sweetie.

216
00:13:05,164 --> 00:13:08,666
This has been hard
on all of us.

217
00:13:08,734 --> 00:13:10,968
But you know he's
gonna visit soon.

218
00:13:11,036 --> 00:13:14,406
Why can't you and Daddy
get married again?

219
00:13:14,473 --> 00:13:18,693
Oh...
I wish we could.

220
00:13:18,761 --> 00:13:20,561
You know, sometimes
mommies and daddies

221
00:13:20,630 --> 00:13:22,664
just can't
be happy together.

222
00:13:22,732 --> 00:13:26,618
I tried to explain
that to her, but...

223
00:13:26,886 --> 00:13:29,270
Are you happy now?

224
00:13:30,839 --> 00:13:32,807
Oh...
[laughs quietly]

225
00:13:32,875 --> 00:13:36,644
