change your name.

237
00:14:26,829 --> 00:14:31,266
You are not some
rock 'n' roll icon
from Liverpool.

238
00:14:31,333 --> 00:14:34,436
You're a dog, and
you shall be named
appropriately.

239
00:14:35,521 --> 00:14:38,472
You will take pride
in this name,

240
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:40,775
and one day,
thank me.

241
00:14:40,843 --> 00:14:45,113
I shall call you...

242
00:14:45,181 --> 00:14:47,131
Spot.

243
00:14:47,199 --> 00:14:48,567
It's a good name...

244
00:14:48,634 --> 00:14:51,552
even though you
don't have spots.

245
00:14:51,620 --> 00:14:52,921
It's not about spots,

246
00:14:52,989 --> 00:14:55,423
as you will come
to understand.

247
00:14:56,359 --> 00:14:58,376
Now,
I expect to witness

248
00:14:58,444 --> 00:15:00,529
the finer side
of your character.

249
00:15:00,596 --> 00:15:03,882
If one of the local
bitches is in heat,

250
00:15:03,950 --> 00:15:05,516
she will remain so,

251
00:15:05,584 --> 00:15:07,752
without any assistance
on your part

252
00:15:07,820 --> 00:15:09,420
to alleviate
her condition.

253
00:15:13,025 --> 00:15:16,244
That's generally
a good way to handle it.

254
00:15:16,312 --> 00:15:18,095
[snuffles]
Oh.

255
00:15:18,331 --> 00:15:21,198
